  "detailed_description": "\"中国象棋-残局\" is a single leisure chess game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game mainly focuses on the classic remnant game of Chinese chess, currently provides 60 levels, followed by nearly 460 levels.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the final game, the principle is \"red first, red must win\". If you go the right way. The red side will surely win. If you miss a step, you will lose everything.",
